column2: Which movies star both Liz Taylor and Richard Burton ?

column2: When was Jack Wolfskin founded ?

column2: Give me all actors who were born in Paris after 1950 .

column5: SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Actor> . ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/birthPlace> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris> . ?uri <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/birthDate> ?date . column2: What is the smallest city by area in Germany ?
